notes:
It's possible to tame this creature by using a [[Golem Wrench]] on it. It's recommended to use your taming item through the [[Battle Window]] to avoid miss clicks since they run a little fast.

Because of their high resistances, they are useful for [[training]] [[Distance]] and [[Melee]] skills using weapons that deal elemental damage. Despite not being really immune to physical damage, their extremely high armor makes it hard to damage them using pure physical attacks.

{{JSpoiler|You need to complete the [[Shadows of Yalahar Quest]] to access them.}}
